Upstream-Name: sjasmplus
Upstream-Contact:
 z00m128 <z00m128@gmail.com>
 ped7g Peter Helcmanovsky <ped@7gods.org>
Source: https://github.com/z00m128/sjasmplus
Files-Excluded:
 lua5.5/*
 docs/documentation.html
 tests/integration/*
 LuaBridge/Tests/*
 LuaBridge/third_party/*
Comment:
 lua5.5/ is standard Lua5.5 bundled in upstream repo for convenience, Debian package is using liblua packages
 documentation.html file is generated by build process, it's part of git repo only for covenience
 tests/integration/ have non-permissive licenses and they are optional tests, not required to build sjasmplus
 LuaBridge/Tests/ and LuaBridge/third_party/ are helper files for the LuaBridge library, not relevant to sjasmplus itself

